paragraphs.text:
%sh

# To access HDFS, needs to get a valid Kerberos ticket first. 
# Replace below parameters:
# YOUR_KEYTAB_FILENAME, your kerberos keytab filename, for example ab1234.keytab
# YOUR_KERBEROS_PRINCIPAL, kerberos principal contained in keytab file, for example ab1234@Hadoop.att.com

kinit -kt /opt/zeppelin/conf/YOUR_KEYTAB_FILENAME YOUR_KERBEROS_PRINCIPAL

klist
